Adds a button to Chrome that redirects you to moone.in on any YouTube video you are watching. On moone.in the video automatically starts in 1080p with annotations set to off.

It is recommended that you use this extension as well (Stop Autoplay for YouTube):
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/stop-autoplay-for-youtube/lgdfnbpkmkkdhgidgcpdkgpdlfjcgnnh
It will stop YouTube from autoplaying the videos so you do not have to pause them before switching to moone.in!
